item.title: Let’s Get This Going
item.description: I’m the least funny guy I know. Among people who actually like me, my “jokes” and humorous remarks kill around 20%. And despite these scientifically accurate calculations, I've decided to go forth and try to create laughing sounds in a quiet room full of drunks. It’s time to get my stand-up “career” under way.
